parameters:
It's been thousands of years since a human came here...
Welcome, child of man.
Memerisu2
Whoa!? Is that some kind of important person?
Thina2
Hey, hey, Memerisu-chan!? That's rude!

It's fine, I don't mind. Child of man, you've done well to
reach this place.
Memerisu1
Right, right! Now, give us the dungeon's treasure!!

Rest assured. My miracle has begun to revolve for you since
the moment you entered this space...
Thina2

Begun to revolve...? We heard that we could get whatever we
desired from the treasure here, but what exactly is this
treasure...?

I am the god who governs the fate of the stars... My miracle
is to turn the stars towards the destiny you desire.
Memerisu1

Miracle? Stars? Destiny...? Sorry, could you please explain
that in Japanese?
Very well.

I govern the fate of all stars and can turn them as many
times as necessary until the desired outcome is achieved.
Until you draw your ideal self... as you wish.

To explain it in terms that humans of this era can
understand, it's like a gacha of miracles.
Memerisu2
Gacha!?
Thina2
That suddenly sounds so mundane...
Memerisu1

Becoming your ideal self sounds amazing! Becoming rich or
having a curvy figure!
Memerisu1

I'm already a super beautiful girl, but I could become even
cuter and be super popular!

It is possible for you to become that star. Now, let us bid
farewell to this life together.
Memerisu2
Eh!! Right now, this life... You mean dying!?
Of course. To redo your star, you must first embrace death.

And no matter how many times you try to redo it, you cannot
reclaim the stars you once abandoned.
Thina2

So that means... no matter how ideal the world or self we
draw, Memerisu-chan and I will never meet again...!
Come now, child of man. Let the miracle be as you wish...
Thina2
Th-that's...
Memerisu1
Memerisu1

I see, if that's the case, I don't need any miracles. Let's
go home, Tina-chan.
Thina1
...!! Memerisu-chan...!!

You refuse the miracle? Why? When you can redo it until you
draw your ideal world, your ideal self.

Especially since you are a gacha addict and a compulsive
spender with a mountain of debt from reckless credit
payments. You can make it as if that addiction and debt
never existed.
Memerisu2

Heh, heh... well, half of that is true. It's a bit painful
to hear...!!
Memerisu2

Any-way! I don't want to be separated from Tina-chan! That's
all! So we're going home now!!
Thina1
Yes, let's go home!

I'm sorry but that is not possible. As I said, the moment
you entered this space, the miracle ≪gacha≫ has started to
turn.

Once my miracle begins to turn the stars, it cannot be
stopped. The only way to stop it is to defeat me, the god
who governs the fate of the stars, and overcome your
destiny.
Memerisu2
Wh-what did you say!?
Memerisu2

Imposing such penance... nothing is more expensive than
something free!
Thina1
Even if our opponent is a god... we will not lose!

Very well... children of man, show me the brilliance of your
stars.
Memerisu2
Damn it all!!!! Getting dragged into such a hassle!!
Memerisu2

What kind of miracle! What kind of gacha! If you're going to
spin it, apologize to me in the afterlife and keep spinning
your apology gacha-!

It's impressive that the children of man have come this
far... However, at this level, my miracle will not stop. The
miracle will soon complete its revolution.
Come, draw forth a new destiny...
Thina2

No way...!! There's no more time... I can't bear to part
with Memerisu-chan...!!
Memerisu2
Grrr...!! In that case... it's time for the last resort!!
Memerisu2

The maximum firepower available on a smartphone, and the
ultimate secret technique! Burn, lithium-ion battery-!!
Child of man, what do you intend to do...!!
Thina2
To cause the battery to overheat... You can't mean...!!
Memerisu2

Ever heard of thermal expansion? A smartphone can explode
with a big bang if it gets too hot!!!
Memerisu2
This is human wisdom! Take this!! Smartphone End Burst!!
Aaaaaaaargh!!!!
\c[31]...Huh? What was I... doing again...

\c[31]...That's right. I'm an adventurer and... I was exploring
dungeons with Tina-chan and... Yes... those were the days...
\c[27]Thump! Thump! Thump! Thump!

Hey, these meat onaholes have been muttering non-stop, are
they broken?

The monster casts a dubious glance at the meat onaholes
muttering nonsense...

The two were purchased as sex slaves at an auction. After
serving various masters, they were sold off to a brothel
where they were continuously embraced, and eventually sold
to a freak show...

Are they dreaming or something...? Maybe I've impregnated
them and made them give birth too much. Even our dicks don't
feel good in them anymore because they're so loose.

In the freak show, the two's nipples and clitorises were
enlarged from training, and their bellies were swollen from
being impregnated and giving birth over and over again...
\c[27]Thump! Thump! Thump! Thump!
\c[27]Squirt! Spurrrtle! Spurt spurt spurt...!!!
\c[17]Ooh... Mmm... Huh...

The two's pussies, continuously violated, easily engulfed
even the large cocks of the monsters, and barely reacted
even when they were creampied...

Damn, this is no good. They're not reacting at all; this
won't get the audience excited.

What should we do... Maybe do another belly punch forced
birth show?

The monsters were at a loss on how to handle the meat
onaholes when the man hosting the freak show started
yelling...!!

Hey! What the hell are you doing?! The audience is getting
bored!!

I'm sorry...!! But these meat onaholes, they're not reacting
at all...

\c[31]Together... dungeon... adventure... walking... hand in
hand...

Huh? Tch, their minds are gone already. Can't be helped...
Hey, prepare for that thing.

The subordinate nods and as he prepares, the host steps in
front of the audience and begins to speak...

Eh-! Ladies and gentlemen! Thank you for waiting! We're
about to show you a special spectacle!!

This is a once-in-a-lifetime event even for a slave! Now, we
will show you what this meat onahole can do...

\c[31](I feel like I can hear something... but it doesn't
matter... because we're in the middle of a fun adventure.)

\c[17](Where shall we go next... always together as best
friends...)

It's unclear where the two began dreaming. It doesn't matter
anymore...

The fun adventure continues in their dreams. All pain and
sadness are forgotten...
...and the two of them felt a lightness in their bodies.

\c[31](...? Somehow my body feels as light as a feather. With
this, we can go anywhere.)

\c[17](Yes, together... just like when we first met, walking hand
in hand.)

They continue to dream a delicate dream that will never come
true as the hell goes on...
The end of this hell... needs no words...

~\c[31]Gacha\c[0] and \c[17]The Holy Maiden\c[0] and
\c[27]The Dangerous Dungeon\c[0]~~BAD END~
一般メスガキ
おっぱい担当

遊ぶ金欲しさにダンジョンにある秘宝を目指して冒険に出た
自称、超絶美少女。スマホより重い物は持ちたくないらしい。

女神のご加護を受けた豊満すぎる聖女。
しかしまだ成長が続いているとの噂も…。

The progress of the Bad End route has been reset! You can
now play the Bad End route from the beginning again.

You have indeed overcome fate. Children of man... surely
you...

Somehow we managed to overcome God's trial and safely escape
the dungeon... but.

\c[17]I'm sorry~~~~~~~~!! It's my fault that Memerisu-chan's
precious smartphone got broken...!!

\c[31]Don't worry about it, Tina-chan! It was my own doing after
all.

\c[17]But... but...!! We didn't get any treasure, and all the
important game data is gone...
\c[17]All that time and money spent... and now it's all gone!
\c[31]...That's true. The smartphone is broken, but... it's okay.

Before we knew it, the sky gradually began to darken, and
beyond the sunset, the starry sky became visible.
\c[31]Ah, look! It's getting dark. Let's go home soon, Tina-chan.

Memerisu-chan smiled shyly while laughing and reached out
her hand to me.
\c[17]*sniffle*... *sob*... Memerisu-chan.

When I took her hand, Memerisu-chan also firmly grasped mine
and we started walking towards home.

\c[31]Walking hand in hand like this reminds me of when I first
met Tina-chan as a child.

\c[31]I found you lost in the forest by chance, and I led you home
by the hand while you were crying your eyes out, Tina-chan!
\c[17]The first time we met... you remember that?
\c[31]Of course I remember! It's an important promise after all.

\c[31]"No matter what comes, it's okay! I'll protect you, so don't
cry."

I thought you had forgotten that nostalgic promise... but
you've remembered it all this time.
\c[31]Oh, look Tina-chan! The stars are out and they're beautiful!
\c[17]Wow... it really is a beautiful night sky!

The night sky we looked up at was beautiful with every
star... as if they were all snuggled up close and connected.

But... even though they seem to be close by, each of these
stars is actually... infinitely far apart.

\c[31]The night roads are dangerous, so make sure to hold on tight
and not let go!

The hand that led me that day is still connected to mine
now.

A story that doesn't save the world or benefit humanity, but
is special to me because it connects me to you.

\c[17]I... I prefer promises over miracles. Choosing a different
star is just... not allowed♥
\c[31]Eh, did you say something? I didn't quite catch that.
\c[17]Fufu, it's a secret♪ Come on, let's go home!

\c[17]*sniffle*... Big sister, I'm scared. What if monsters
appear...
\c[31]It's okay, it's okay! I'm very strong!

\c[31]No matter what comes, it's okay! I'll protect you, so don't
cry. I promise!
\c[17]*sob*... *sniffle*... uhh... really?
Rustle! Rustle rustle!!
Croak, croak...
\c[17]Ah, it's a frog...

\c[31]Wha-wha-what! It's just a frog! I'm not scared! I'm the
strongest, so there's no way I'd lose!!
\c[17]...Pfft. Fufu... Fufufu.

\c[31]Hey! Don't laugh! Geez... But you stopped crying, so that's
good!
\c[31]I'm Memerisu! What's your name?
\c[17]I'm Tina!

\c[31]Alright, Tina-chan! Follow me! Let's search for the exit in
the forest together! It's probably over there!
\c[17]Feh!? Memerisu-chan, you're lost too!?

\c[31]If we're together, there's nothing to be afraid of! Now, our
adventure begins!!

~\c[31]Gacha\c[0] and \c[17]Saintess\c[0] and
\c[27]Dangerous Dungeon\c[0]~ The End

Gained the True Smartphone of Memories and the True Grimoire
